  title="Why You Do the Thing You Don't Want to Do"
  lead="A short guide to the gap between what you feel and how you act."
  metaTitle="Why You Do the Thing You Don't Want to Do — Ennea Evolution"
  metaDescription="The behavior you can't seem to stop is doing a job. Three questions that turn self-criticism into information."
  startHeading="If this named something real"
  start="The work I do with people goes exactly here: finding what your pattern is protecting, and helping it update, so the change holds."
